title: Shake Them Ropes - Wrestling Podcast - 4/15/2014
description:
Shake Them Ropes 
April 15, 2014 

Podcast 

Rob & Jeff talk the happenings of WWE coming out of Raw and leading towards Extreme Rules. What is the real main event of Extreme Rules, who will battle Big E for the Intercontinental Championship, and we wish Austin Aries a happy birthday. Plus, Jeff gives us his odds on certain superstars chances of appearing on WWE Raw this year, from Sami Zayn to Chris Sabin of all people.
